00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:23.710
You were there taking pictures.

00:15:23.710 --> 00:15:26.610
What's your view on
things like YouTube

00:15:26.610 --> 00:15:28.280
and Snapchat and Facebook?

00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:29.581
What's your view on them?

00:15:29.581 --> 00:15:31.830
DANNY FIELDS: Facebook was
a nightmare for a few days.

00:15:31.830 --> 00:15:34.860
And I said, get
this out of my life.

00:15:34.860 --> 00:15:37.670
This is horrible.

00:15:37.670 --> 00:15:39.960
I don't like what it does.

00:15:39.960 --> 00:15:43.190
And my friends are going to
be people I know and like

00:15:43.190 --> 00:15:46.790
and want to hug, and
be with, and talk to.

00:15:46.790 --> 00:15:50.860
And what I say to my friends I
could not say to anyone else.

00:15:50.860 --> 00:15:52.500
That's what the
definition of a friend

00:15:52.500 --> 00:15:56.230
is-- you can communicate
with-- so I'm not going public

00:15:56.230 --> 00:15:58.870
with my-- what's in my heart.

00:15:58.870 --> 00:16:02.260
That required that
disconnect-- which, I can't.

00:16:02.260 --> 00:16:04.140
It's still there.

00:16:04.140 --> 00:16:07.360
I still get alerts from them.

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:10.570
And then someone
else put me on there.

00:16:10.570 --> 00:16:12.700
