00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:17.630
it's going to be there.

00:16:17.630 --> 00:16:18.730
But just-- no.

00:16:18.730 --> 00:16:20.560
I have-- no.

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:24.980
I have enough wonderful friends
