00:16:48.730 --> 00:16:49.710
[LAUGHTER]

00:16:49.710 --> 00:16:51.436
And the rest is bullshit.

00:16:51.436 --> 00:16:52.560
It's a bunch of commentary.

00:16:52.560 --> 00:16:54.840
