Every once in a
while, there's going

00:17:21.790 --> 00:17:23.869
to be something--
oh, this is great.

00:17:23.869 --> 00:17:26.810
But I don't care.

00:17:26.810 --> 00:17:29.350
Take it away-- Snapchat.

00:17:29.350 --> 00:17:31.837
Don't take away my
YouTube or my Google.

00:17:31.837 --> 00:17:33.420
FIONNUALA MEEHAN:
We will not do that.

00:17:33.420 --> 00:17:37.030
DANNY FIELDS: Facebook
and-- it's a menace.

00:17:37.030 --> 00:17:38.880
It only causes trouble.

00:17:38.880 --> 00:17:44.610
The only-- people I love and
respect-- I can't name names.

00:17:44.610 --> 00:17:47.240
A wonderful woman, who's
a very, very old, dear

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:51.130
friend, who's a great
international performer

00:17:51.130 --> 00:17:52.700
