What?

00:18:05.050 --> 00:18:07.620
They love what you
had for breakfast?

00:18:07.620 --> 00:18:09.160
You're you.

00:18:09.160 --> 00:18:12.380
You're an artist, you're a
performer, you're amazing.

00:18:12.380 --> 00:18:15.330
They love what you
had for-- and you

00:18:15.330 --> 00:18:19.770
