stage, get naked, or talk

00:18:30.700 --> 00:18:35.180
about what's corrupt and
what's evil and what's good.

00:18:35.180 --> 00:18:37.180
I don't want to know what
you had for breakfast.

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:41.122
And I certainly don't know why
