00:19:17.840 --> 00:19:19.315
difficult for some people.

00:19:19.315 --> 00:19:20.190
DANNY FIELDS: I know.

00:19:20.190 --> 00:19:24.860
I don't-- I was born out.

00:19:24.860 --> 00:19:27.890
I don't know what
that means-- come out.

00:19:27.890 --> 00:19:29.660
