say, Mom-- well,

00:19:43.985 --> 00:19:46.260
what-- Mom found a letter.

00:19:46.260 --> 00:19:46.760
OK.

00:19:46.760 --> 00:19:48.020
You know, this happens.

00:19:48.020 --> 00:19:49.040
And then, yeah.

00:19:49.040 --> 00:19:53.320
I mean, it's all-- can't
be a surprise, Mom.

00:19:53.320 --> 00:19:56.610
It's what you always
feared, expected, dreaded.

00:19:56.610 --> 00:19:57.230
Yeah.

00:19:57.230 --> 00:19:58.600
Let's move on.

00:19:58.600 --> 00:20:05.000
So I-- saying that and being
dismissive about it makes

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:09.610
me think, well, there's someone
there in the middle of nowhere

00:20:09.610 --> 00:20:14.360
who is ashamed,
concerned, depressed,

00:20:14.360 --> 00:20:18.780
confused about his
or her sexuality.

00:20:18.780 --> 00:20:22.140
Which now, has got-- you've
got 15 niches of that.

00:20:22.140 --> 00:20:24.720
