week, there's a new letter.

00:20:27.990 --> 00:20:32.380
So I just call it BLT. And
everyone knows what that means.

00:20:32.380 --> 00:20:36.850
And it sort of has
everything in it.

00:20:36.850 --> 00:20:39.420
I can't follow this jewel--
if you're less talented, ugh!

00:20:42.200 --> 00:20:42.900
This niche.

00:20:42.900 --> 00:20:45.130
I don't know.

00:20:45.130 --> 00:20:47.650
