cynical here.

00:20:47.650 --> 00:20:53.730
My heart is with anyone who
feels that they are not--

00:20:53.730 --> 00:20:56.460
don't deserve to be a
human being because of whom

00:20:56.460 --> 00:20:58.030
they love.

00:20:58.030 --> 00:21:00.770
And what bodies
they want to hold.

00:21:00.770 --> 00:21:03.590
And what they want to touch.

00:21:03.590 --> 00:21:05.360
All that.

00:21:05.360 --> 00:21:06.640
Who made those rules?

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:07.250
Nobody.

00:21:07.250 --> 00:21:09.230
We don't need to reproduce.

00:21:09.230 --> 00:21:11.150
Because that's
where we came from.

00:21:11.150 --> 00:21:15.923
And we're living with a very
unfortunate set of biblical--

00:21:15.923 --> 00:21:19.950
some people wandering through
a desert, saying, do this.

00:21:19.950 --> 00:21:22.070
Don't do that.

00:21:22.070 --> 00:21:23.420
Not me.

00:21:23.420 --> 00:21:24.740
Not modern.

00:21:24.740 --> 00:21:29.519
But I can't do any good by
saying these things, can I?

00:21:29.519 --> 00:21:31.310
I just sound like, oh,
you'll be all right.

00:21:31.310 --> 00:21:31.930
Look at me.

00:21:31.930 --> 00:21:32.900
I'm fine.

00:21:32.900 --> 00:21:38.180
I, famously-- I read in
a "Village Voice" story

00:21:38.180 --> 00:21:39.900
that I was famously gay.

00:21:39.900 --> 00:21:42.275
Famously gay, what
does that mean?

00:21:42.275 --> 00:21:43.970
[LAUGHTER]

00:21:45.350 --> 00:21:47.280
It was about a
Bette Midler show.

00:21:47.280 --> 00:21:49.720
Even people who
are famously gay,

00:21:49.720 --> 00:21:55.180
like me, hugged and
kissed her after the show.

00:21:55.180 --> 00:21:59.800
What does famously gay-- how
can you-- what does that mean?

00:21:59.800 --> 00:22:00.980
But that's what it means.

00:22:00.980 --> 00:22:06.160
And do what you want and I
will, hopefully, do what I want.

00:22:06.160 --> 00:22:08.030
Which is, right now,
have some water.

00:22:08.030 --> 00:22:08.530
FIONNUALA MEEHAN:
Have some water.

00:22:08.530 --> 00:22:09.860
DANNY FIELDS: Because that
was hard going through that.

00:22:09.860 --> 00:22:10.930
FIONNUALA MEEHAN: Yeah.

