That was-- no, thank you for--

00:22:12.630 --> 00:22:14.088
DANNY FIELDS: It's
not a Facebook--

00:22:14.088 --> 00:22:19.313
it's not-- I thought, I can't
promulgate these things.

00:22:19.313 --> 00:22:23.230
It's not a papal
